      "title": "Eggs for wholesale traders at Rs. 46/-",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The All Ceylon Poultry Businessmen's Association says that it has decided to sell an egg for Rs.46/- for wholesale traders who visit Poultry Farms.",
        "The Chairman of the All Ceylon Poultry Businessmen's Association Ajith Gunasekara said that the sale of eggs has dropped on recent weeks.",
        "He said that the government has been requested to provide benefits for the egg producers until the issued gazette is revised.",
        "China says it will support consultations for SL debt solution"
      ],
